sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant Pool
participant DB
participant Logger

User->>Frontend: Update booking
Frontend->>API: PATCH /api/bookings/:bookingId
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: Validate bookingId and actor employee id
alt Invalid booking id
API-->>Frontend: 400 Invalid booking id
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Valid booking id
alt Invalid authenticated user
API-->>Frontend: 401 Invalid authenticated user
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Valid user
API->>Pool: getConnection + beginTransaction
API->>DB: Select booking FOR UPDATE
alt Booking not found
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 404 Booking not found
Frontend-->>User: Show not found
else Booking found
API->>API: Check permission (organizer or admin)
alt Not allowed
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 403 You do not have permission to edit this booking
Frontend-->>User: Show forbidden
else Allowed
API->>API: Check status (cancelled/vacated)
alt Cancelled or vacated
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 Booking cannot be edited
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Status ok
API->>API: Validate participant list
alt Invalid participant list
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 participant_employee_ids validation error
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Participants valid
API->>API: Validate title/description/start/end
alt Missing required fields
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 title, description, start_time, end_time are required
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Fields valid
alt end_time <= start_time
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 end_time must be greater than start_time
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Time order valid
alt Past booking edit
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 You can only edit future bookings
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Time ok
API->>DB: Fetch organizer employee
alt Organizer not found
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 404 Organizer employee was not found
Frontend-->>User: Show not found
else Organizer ok
API->>DB: Fetch participants if provided
alt Participants invalid or inactive
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 One or more participant employees are invalid or inactive
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Participants ok
API->>DB: Lock employees for scheduling
API->>DB: Select room FOR UPDATE
alt Room not found
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 404 Room not found
Frontend-->>User: Show not found
else Room found
API->>DB: Check room capacity
alt Capacity exceeded
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 400 Total attendees cannot exceed room capacity
Frontend-->>User: Show validation error
else Capacity ok
API->>DB: Check room conflict
alt Room already booked
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 409 Room is already booked for the selected time slot
Frontend-->>User: Show conflict
else Room available
API->>DB: Validate employee scheduling conflicts
alt Attendee conflicts
API->>Pool: rollback
API-->>Frontend: 409 Scheduling conflicts
Frontend-->>User: Show conflict details
else No conflicts
API->>DB: Sync participants (if provided)
API->>DB: Update booking
API->>DB: Insert booking audit
API->>Logger: booking_participants_updated (if applicable)
API->>Pool: commit
API-->>Frontend: 200 Booking updated successfully
Frontend-->>User: Show success
end
